---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Content from "../../layouts/Content.astro";
const pageScript = "/js/pages/web/unit-converter.js";
---
<Layout title="Unit Converter | TechRegistry"><Content title="Unit Converter" titleTag="Web" starCount="4.6k stars" usageCount="6.8k uses today" version="v2.7.1" statusText="All Systems Operational" freeLabel="100% Free" privacyLabel="Client-Side Only" poweredBy="browser-side JS" breadcrumbs={[{ label: "Home", href: "/" }, { label: "Unit Converter" }]}><div class="tool-page-shell" id="tool-page-root"><div class="card"><div class="card-body"><div class="tool-toolbar"><button id="tool-load-sample" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-sm" type="button">Load Sample</button><button id="tool-clear" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm" type="button">Clear</button><button id="tool-run" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" type="button">Convert</button></div><div class="tool-field-grid mt-3 mb-3"><div><label class="form-label" for="unit-mode">Mode</label><select id="unit-mode" class="form-select" data-tool-field="mode"><option value="px-rem">px to rem</option><option value="rem-px">rem to px</option><option value="hex-rgb">HEX to RGB</option><option value="rgb-hex">RGB to HEX</option></select></div><div><label class="form-label" for="unit-value">Value</label><input id="unit-value" class="form-control" data-tool-field="value" /></div><div><label class="form-label" for="unit-base">Base</label><input id="unit-base" class="form-control" data-tool-field="base" value="16" /></div></div><div id="tool-status" class="tool-status">Ready.</div><div class="mt-3"><div class="tool-label-row"><label class="form-label mb-0">Converted Output</label><span class="text-body-secondary">Result appears here</span></div><pre id="tool-output" class="tool-code-output tool-code-output-compact"></pre></div><div id="tool-detail-panel" hidden class="mt-3"><div class="tool-label-row"><label class="form-label mb-0">Notes</label><span class="text-body-secondary">Conversion details</span></div><pre id="tool-detail-output" class="tool-detail-output"></pre></div></div></div><div class="card tool-details-card"><div class="card-header"><h3 class="card-title">About This Unit Converter</h3></div><div class="card-body"><p>This unit converter helps with common frontend sizing and color conversions such as px and rem or HEX and RGB values.</p><p>It is useful during CSS work, design handoff, and layout tuning when you need quick trustworthy conversions.</p><ul class="tool-detail-list"><li>Supports px/rem and HEX/RGB conversion modes.</li><li>Helpful for CSS and design system work.</li><li>Uses fast browser-side conversion logic.</li></ul></div></div></div></Content></Layout><script type="module" src={pageScript}></script>
